[Patient] What should I do if I forget to track my fluid intake for a day?
[Educator] Try to estimate your intake as best as you can and resume tracking the next day.
[Patient] Thank you for all the information on managing my fluid intake with heart failure.
[Educator] You're welcome! Remember to take control of your health and reach out if you have any concerns.